#: canteen/views.py:77
msgid ""
"Formats like \"YYYY.mm.dd\", \"YYYY/mm/dd\", \"YYYY.mm.dd\", \"mm/dd\", "
"\"mmdd\", and \"mm.dd\" are all acceptable. In short, FNSCHOOL wants to be "
"compatible with all the formats you like, but if something goes wrong, you "
"have to tell the developers. Thank you!"
msgstr ""
"像这样的格式都能行：“年年年年-月月-日日”、“年年年年/月月/日日”、“年年年年.月"
"月.日日”、“月月-日日”、“月月日日”，“月月.日日” 。总之，FNSCHOOL 想兼容所有你"
"喜欢的格式，但是如果出错了，你要告诉开发者，谢谢你！"

#: canteen/views.py:85
msgid "Name of Ingredient"
msgstr "食材名称"

#: canteen/views.py:89
msgid ""
"For example, breakfast, dinner, regular meals, nutritious meals, etc., when "
"generating a spreadsheet, each meal category corresponds to a spread sheet. "
"If left blank, only one spreadsheet will be generated."
msgstr ""
"比如早餐、晚餐、正餐、营养餐等，生成 表册 的时候每个餐类对应着一个 表册  。不"
"填的话只生成一个 表册 。"

#: canteen/views.py:97
msgid "Category"
msgstr "食材大类"

#: canteen/views.py:99
msgid ""
"Usually there are seven categories: vegetables, meat, grains, seasonings, "
"eggs and milk, oils, and fruits."
msgstr ""
"通常是七大类：蔬菜类、肉类、粮食类、调味类、蛋奶和糕点类、油类、水果类。"

#: canteen/views.py:104
msgid "Quantity"
msgstr "数量"

#: canteen/views.py:106
msgid ""
"To prevent the number of decimal places in the unit price from becoming too "
"large, \"quantity\" is only allowed to be an integer. If your unit price is "
"a decimal, please use a smaller quantity unit and then expand the quantity "
"to an integer."
msgstr ""
"为防止单价的小数位数变得很多，“数量”只允许为整数。如果你的单价是小数，请你用"
"更小的数量单位，然后把数量扩大为整数。"

#: canteen/views.py:117
msgid "Total Price"
msgstr "总价"

#: canteen/views.py:121
msgid "Unit Name of Quantity"
msgstr "数量单位"

#: canteen/views.py:125
msgid "Is Ignorable"
msgstr "是不用入库的"

#: canteen/views.py:126
msgid "As long as a cell has content, it will be considered as \"yes\"."
msgstr "只要单元格有内容，就会被当作“是”。"

